20square%20of%20good-quality%20chocolate%20if%20I%20want%20something%20sweet%2C%20and%20I%20do%20try%20to%20follow%20a%20keto-%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffavorite-mediterranean-diet-meals-to-prep-from-someone-followed-years%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20eat%20at%20fast%20food%20places%2C%20and%20if%20I%20do%20go%20out%20to%20eat%2C%20I%20try%20to%20eat%20as%20I%20would%20at%20home%2C%20but%20that%20is%20harder%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226468b0e1-00d6-4194-9cf5-a302227a278b%5C%22%3EMake%20small%20swaps%20to%20reduce%20calories%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMockler%20said%20that%20Erstad's%20diet%20is%20%26quot%3Bvery%20nutritious%26quot%3B%20thanks%20to%20all%20the%20plants%2C%20quality%20proteins%2C%20and%20whole%20foods%20she%20eats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20one%20of%20her%20goals%20is%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20we%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20quantity%20of%20her%20calorie%20intake%2C%26quot%3B%20Mockler%20said%20via%20email.%20%26quot%3BSomething%20I%20see%20quite%20often%20is%20people%20consuming%20a%20lot%20of%20healthy%20foods%20but%20forgetting%20that%20those%20foods%20contain%20calories%2C%20too%2C%20and%20can%20still%20be%20overeaten%20(in%20terms%20of%20weight%20management).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20breakfast%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Erstad%20could%20consider%20eating%20one%20teaspoon%20each%20of%20seeds%20and%20nuts%20rather%20than%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20could%20also%20swap%20dried%20fruit%20for%20fresh%2C%20which%20is%20more%20filling%20and%20higher%20volume%20for%20fewer%20calories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErstad's%20go-to%20snacks%20are%20nutritious%2C%20but%20the%20quantity%20could%20be%20preventing%20her%20from%20losing%20weight%2C%20as%20peanut%20butter%20and%20nuts%20are%20energy-dense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLittle%20decreases%20in%20her%20portions%20throughout%20the%20day%20at%20each%20meal%20can%20add%20up%20big%20time%20and%20reduce%20her%20overall%20calorie%20intake%20by%20300-500%20calories%20per%20day%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20weight%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Mockler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22475c0eb1-2ea3-4243-a37e-4421565e0b53%5C%22%3ELift%20weights%20to%20build%20strength%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMockler%20said%20a%20few%20tweaks%20to%20Erstad's%20fitness%20routine%20would%20help%20her%20achieve%20her%20fitness%20goals..%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrength-training-women-benefits-lift-weights-celebrity-personal-trainer-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrength%20training%3C%2Fa%3E%20twice%20a%20week%20would%20be%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%20%E2%80%94%20Mockler%20recommended%20swapping%20one%20hour%20of%20her%20HIIT%20or%20Pilates%20workouts%20for%20two%2030-minute%20full-body%20lifting%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncluding%20cardio%20(her%20HIIT%20workouts)%2C%20pilates%20(great%20for%20flexibility)%2C%20and%20lifting%20(strength)%20will%20give%20her%20a%20well-rounded%20workout%20routine%2C%26quot%3B%20Mockler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20Erstad%20would%20also%20try%20to%20move%20more%20in%20general%2C%20despite%20her%20sedentary%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20more%20steps%20or%20non-exercise%20movement%20would%20not%20only%20be%20good%20for%20her%20overall%20health%20but%20would%20likely%20help%20with%20her%20goal%20of%20weight%20loss%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Mockler%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'd%20recommend%20adding%202%2C000%20steps%20to%20whatever%20her%20current%20daily%20step%20average%20is%20right%20now%20as%20a%20goal.%20Then%20in%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20she%20can%20try%20to%20increase%20her%20step%20average%20again%20until%20she%20is%20around%207%2C000%20to%2010%2C000%20steps%20per%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECreating%20habits%20like%20parking%20further%20away%20from%20your%20destination%2C%20getting%20up%20from%20your%20desk%20every%20hour%2C%20using%20stairs%20rather%20than%20elevators%2C%20and%20getting%20a%20walking%20pad%20can%20help%2C%20Mockler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20I%20think%20Joanne's%20diet%20is%20very%20nutritious%20and%20her%20fitness%20routine%20is%20in%20a%20good%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20Mockler%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20small%20tweaks%20to%20both%20(decreasing%20portion%20sizes%2C%20adding%20strength%20training%2C%20and%20increasing%20steps)%2C%20she%20will%20be%20well%20on%20her%20way%20to%20her%20goals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flose-weight-build-strength-simple-food-swaps-lift-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748521292000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838467dca50259add4d46e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flose-weight-build-strength-simple-food-swaps-lift-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20already%20eating%20a%20nutritious%20diet%20but%20struggling%20to%20lose%20weight%2C%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20portion%20sizes%20and%20try%20to%20move%20more%2C%20the%20dietitian%20Kara%20Mockler%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flose-weight-build-strength-simple-food-swaps-lift-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Til%20death%20do%20us%20part%3A%20Why%20couples%20are%20killing%20instead%20of%20leaving%20partners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748521099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121491287%2Cimgsize-3968547.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fabuse-denial-death-whats-behind-the-surge-in-killings-of-husbands-in-india-experts-reveal-missed-signs%