%20exports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20seemingly%20wants%20to%20get%20their%20hands%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwatches-smartest-investment-resale-market-rolex-patek-phillipe-piguet-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eluxury%20watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-do-trump-tariffs-work-what-are-tariffs-trump-plan-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fhs.swiss%2Ffile%2F59%2Fcomm_250404_a.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Federation%20of%20the%20Swiss%20Watch%20Industry%20found%20that%20Swiss%20watch%20exports%20grew%20by%2018.2%25%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20accounted%20for%20nearly%20%241.03%20billion%20(851.9%20million%20Swiss%20francs)%20in%20watch%20imports%2C%20propping%20up%20an%20otherwise%20struggling%20global%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20surge%20in%20Swiss%20watch%20exports%20to%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%26quot%3Bmainly%20the%20result%20of%20early%20shipments%2C%20motivated%20by%20the%20increase%20in%20US%20customs%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20federation%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20surge%20in%20Swiss%20watch%20exports%20to%20the%20US%2C%20despite%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Trump-era%20tariffs%2C%20is%20a%20clear%20indication%20of%20the%20unique%20resilience%20and%20desirability%20of%20luxury%20timepieces%20among%20affluent%20American%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Andrew%20Du%20Plessis%2C%20commercial%20director%20for%20the%20Luxury%20Network%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeri%20Karra%20Sillaman%2C%20author%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Expert%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Oxford's%20Said%20Business%20School%2C%20told%20BI%2C%20that%20the%20watch%20industry%20is%20seeing%20a%20rise%20in%20interest%E2%80%94not%20just%20from%20traditional%20collectors%20but%20also%20from%20first-time%20buyers%20treating%20timepieces%20as%20hard%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federation%20observed%20watches%20with%20an%20export%20price%20above%20%243%2C600%20(3%2C000%20francs)%20%26quot%3Bset%20the%20tone%2C%20with%20growth%20of%2022.9%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Patek%2C%20a%20Royal%20Oak%2C%20or%20even%20a%20well-kept%20vintage%20piece%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20investment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neri%20Karra%20Sillaman.%20%26quot%3BIn%20times%20of%20economic%20volatility%2C%20people%20are%20putting%20their%20money%20into%20things%20they%20believe%20will%20hold%20value%E2%80%94just%20like%20gold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20trust%20the%20value%20of%20a%20Rolex%20or%20a%20Patek%20Philippe%20more%20than%20a%20volatile%20stock%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20April%202%2C%20Trump%20announced%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bliberation%20day%26quot%3B%20tariffs%20targeting%20Swiss-made%20goods%2C%20including%20luxury%20watches.%20While%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-says-trumps-baseline-10-tariff-here-to-stay-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaseline%20rate%20is%2010%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Swiss%20exports%20could%20face%20tariffs%20as%20high%20as%2031%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20growth%20drivers%20by%20value%20were%20watches%20made%20from%20precious%20metals%2C%20steel%2Fgold-steel%2C%20and%20bimetallic%20watches%20%E2%80%94%20materials%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-us-trump-trade-war-tariffs-countermeasures-aluminum-steel-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etargeted%20by%20Trump's%20additional%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-watches-more-expensive-trump-tariffs-switzerland-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eanalysts%20said%20could%20make%20buying%20a%20Rolex%20even%20more%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteel%20watches%20led%20to%20an%20increase%2