f%20subtle%20erosion%20of%20humanity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20his%20theory%20of%20friendship%20was%20%26quot%3Btwo%20people%20agree%20to%20help%20each%20other%20become%20the%20best%20versions%20of%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20dynamic%20that%20involves%20not%20just%20emotional%20support%2C%20but%20also%20accountability%20%E2%80%94%20something%20no%20chatbot%20can%20reciprocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20only%2C%20'Are%20you%20there%20for%20me%3F'%2C%20but%20I%20am%20here%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20praised%20design%20choices%20like%20Inflection%20AI's%20Pi%20assistant%2C%20which%20explicitly%20tells%20users%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20your%20companion%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20encourages%20people%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20actual%20human%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHelping%20you%20go%20out%20into%20your%20world%20of%20friends%20is%2C%20I%20think%2C%20an%20extremely%20important%20thing%20for%20a%20companion%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20tech%20companies%20race%20to%20deploy%20more%20emotionally%20intelligent%20bots%2C%20Hoffman%20argued%20for%20more%20transparency%20and%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20as%20a%20market%20should%20demand%20it%2C%20we%20as%20an%20industry%2C%20all%20MPAs%2C%20should%20standardize%20around%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20there's%20confusion%20around%20this%2C%20I%20think%20we%20as%20government%20should%20say%2C%20'Hey%2C%20look%2C%20if%20you're%20not%20stepping%20up%20to%20this%2C%20we%20should.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Hoffman%2C%20the%20stakes%20are%20high.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20a%20degradation%20of%20the%20quality%20of%20elevation%20of%20human%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20should%20not%20be%20what%20it's%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoffman%20isn't%20alone%20in%20raising%20the%20alarm%20on%20AI%20companions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20Senate%20testimony%20earlier%20this%20