EStarting%20June%2024%2C%20the%20coffee%20chain%20will%20scrap%20its%20bonus%20for%20customers%20who%20bring%20their%20personal%2C%20reusable%20cup%20to%20stores.%20Currently%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-offer-fewer-deals-under-new-ceo-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20Rewards%3C%2Fa%3E%20members%20get%2025%20stars%20for%20bringing%20their%20own%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Rewards%20members%20who%20use%20their%20own%20cup%20will%20earn%20double%20the%20stars%20on%20their%20entire%20order.%20At%20its%20most%20basic%20Rewards%20tier%2C%20Starbucks%20Rewards%20members%20get%20one%20star%20for%20every%20dollar%20that%20they%20spend%20before%20sales%20tax.%20Members%20can%20redeem%20stars%20for%20free%20food%20and%20beverages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Starbucks%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20the%20planned%20change%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20that%20the%20company%20will%20continue%20to%20offer%20a%20%240.10%20discount%20as%20well%20when%20customers%20bring%20in%20their%20reusable%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20means%20that%20Starbucks%20customers%20who%20tend%20to%20order%20a%20single%20drink%20when%20they%20stop%20by%20could%20earn%20rewards%20more%20slowly%20under%20the%20change.%20Under%20the%20current%20system%2C%20a%20beverage%20that%20normally%20earns%20nine%20stars%20would%20earn%20an%20extra%2025%20if%20a%20customer%20brings%20in%20their%20own%20cup%20for%20a%20total%20of%2034%2C%20for%20example.%20With%20the%20change%2C%20the%20same%20order%20would%20earn%2018%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Reddit%20page%20devoted%20to%20Starbucks%2C%20one%20poster%20said%20that%20they%20were%20accustomed%20to%20getting%20the%20bonus%20on%20their%20regular%20coffee%20run.%20%26quot%3BHonestly%20the%2025%20stars%20is%20what%20keeps%20me%20going%20back%20daily%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Fstarbucks%2Fcomments%2F1kvxq0u%2Fno_more_25_stars_for_personal_cup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20reads%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20saving%20my%20stars%20for%20when%20I%20go%20on%20vacation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20who%20order%20sandwiches%20or%20other%20food%20items%2C%20which%20tend%20to%20cost%20more%20than%20beverages%20and%20thus%20earn%20more%20stars%2C%20could%20earn%20rewards%20more%20quickly%20with%20the%20change%2C%20meanwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20change%20that%20Starbucks%20has%20made%20in%20the%20last%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Brian%20Niccol%20became%20CEO%20in%20September%2C%20Starbucks%20has%20made%20numerous%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanges-coming-to-starbucks-sales-free-refills-fewer-app-rewards-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echanges%20at%20its%20cafes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20chain%20has%20trimmed%20its%20menu%20options%2C%20added%20shifts%20at%20some%20stores%2C%20and%20now%20asks%20baristas%20to%20leave%20customers%20handwritten%20messages%20on%20single-use%20cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20offers%20incentives%20for%20customers%20to%20bring%20their%20own%20reusable%20cups%2C%20including%20the%2025-star%20bonus%20and%20the%20%240.10%20discount%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20single-use%20plastics%20and%20paper%20cups.%20The%20chain%20extended%20the%20incentives%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.starbucks.com%2Fpress%2F2024%2Fstarbucks-becomes-first-national-coffee-retailer-to-accept-reusable-cups-for-drive-thru-and-mobile-orders%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrive-thru%20and%20mobile%20orders%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Starbucks%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2