-jerry-talton-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegal%20battle%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Carta%20and%20Talton%2C%20who%20accused%20Carta%20of%20whistleblower%20retaliation%20and%20defamation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaur%20emailed%20the%20detailed%2C%20two-page%20letter%20to%20Carta's%20CEO%2C%20general%20counsel%2C%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20and%20Talton%20himself.%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20Kaur%20alleged%20that%20Ward%20made%20her%20feel%20%26quot%3Bvulnerable%20and%20smaller%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20dinner%20with%20him%2C%20ignored%20a%20potential%20promotion%2C%20and%20used%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Bceremonial%26quot%3B%20to%20describe%20part%20of%20her%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25955962-kaur-resignation-letter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOctober%202022%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20part%20of%20evidence%20for%20Talton's%20claims%20that%20Carta%20had%20a%20culture%20of%20gender%20discrimination.%20Kaur%20told%20BI%20that%20while%20the%20dinner%20with%20Ward%20did%20happen%2C%20she%20misperceived%20Ward's%20comments.%20She%20praised%20Ward's%20leadership%20and%20her%20time%20at%20Carta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20wanted%20to%20clarify%2C%20I%20was%20emotional%20and%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20going%20on%20at%20the%20company%20with%20exec%20turnover%20and%20whatnot%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaur%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BMisunderstandings%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarta%2C%20which%20encouraged%20BI%20to%20speak%20with%20Kaur%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Kaur%20was%20initially%20persuaded%20by%20Talton%20to%20send%20the%20resignation%20letter%20during%20a%20time%20she%20testified%20was%20'emotional%20and%20difficult.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTalton's%20attempt%20to%20connect%20her%20resignation%20with%20his%20termination%20to%20draw%20conclusions%20about%20culture%20at%20Carta%20is%20a%20gross%20distortion%20of%20the%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20Carta%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETalton%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarta%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20helps%20companies%20manage%20employee%20equity%20and%20shares%2C%20has%20raised%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20VCs%20such%20as%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20and%20Lightspeed%20Venture%20Partners.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20it%20has%20faced%20numerous%20complaints%20and%20lawsuits%2C%20many%20of%20which%20focused%20on%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcarta-lawsuits-employees-ceo-retaliation-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWard%20and%20his%20conduct.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228841c83c-d671-46fe-85d1-0a90e4c83286%5C%22%3E'A%20pattern%20of%20humiliating%20certain%20women'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaur's%20letter%20attributes%20her%20resignation%20to%20a%20humiliating%20dinner%20with%20Ward%20in%20October%202022%2C%20during%20which%20he%20made%20comments%20that%20%26quot%3Bconvinced%26quot%3B%20her%20she%20could%20no%20longer%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaur%20loved%20working%20at%20Carta%20and%20admired%20Ward%2C%20the%20email%20says.%20She%20wanted%20to%20help%20the%20company%20during%20a%20turbulent%20period%20marked%20by%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20the%20departure%20of%20chief%20product%20officer%20Heidi%20Johnson%2C%20and%20its%20CTO%2C%20Talton%2C%20being%20placed%20on%20leave.%20A%20few%20months%20later%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funicorn-carta-lawsuit-cto-gender-discrimination-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarta%20sued%20Talton%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20secretly%20recording%20meetings%2C%20sparking%20the%20current%20legal%20battle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20says%20Ward%20made%20Kaur%20feel%20%26quot%3Bvulnerable%20and%20smaller%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20showed%20no%20interest%20in%20her%20contributions%20or%20ideas%20and%20sidestepped%20a%20conversation%20about%20promoting%20her%20to%20senior%20vice%