ndi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fmaa-trailer-the-intriguing-trailer-with-shaitaan-vibe-sees-kajol-fights-with-rakshas-to-save-her-daughter-watch-video%2Farticleshow%2F121485495.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20This%20Delhi-Based%20Company%20Saved%204.5%20Million%20Milk%20Packets%20From%20Ending%20Up%20in%20Landfills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20plastic%20has%20been%20both%20a%20marvel%20and%20a%20menace.%20Introduced%20to%20India%20in%20the%20mid-20th%20century%2C%20plastic%20quickly%20became%20a%20popular%20alternative%20to%20traditional%20materials%20due%20to%20its%20durability%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20low%20cost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20it%20found%20its%20way%20into%20every%20aspect%20of%20life%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F319630%2Fdesigner-turns-waste-material-into-eco-friendly-furniture-ek-kalakar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epackaging%20and%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20infrastructure%20and%20fashion.%20But%20what%20once%20symbolised%20innovation%20has%20now%20become%20one%20of%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20environmental%20threats.%20India%20alone%20generates%20over%203.4%20million%20tonnes%20of%20plastic%20waste%20annually%2C%20much%20of%20it%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20or%20choking%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20not%20everyone%20sees%20plastic%20as%20the%20villain.%20%E2%80%9CPlastic%2C%20for%20me%2C%20is%20not%20a%20bad%20material%3B%20it%20is%20the%20poor%20disposal%20and%20not%20repurposing%20it%20that%20creates%20a%20huge%20issue%20for%20the%20planet%20and%20the%20natural%20resources%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Yuvraj%20Singh%20Ahuja%2C%20architect-turned-entrepreneur%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%E2%80%98Sereno%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tr