onomy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20Sereno%20began%20experimenting%20with%20post-consumer%20waste%3A%20milk%20bags%2C%20shampoo%20bottles%2C%20and%20single-use%20plastics%2C%20before%20they%20could%20reach%20landfills.%20The%20team%20cracked%20a%20formula%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F397387%2Fbihar-brothers-transform-plastic-waste-into-stunning-eco-friendly-furniture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretain%20durability%20and%20aesthetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20using%20repurposed%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22recycling%20process%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440447%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20hard-to-recycle%20plastic%20is%20converted%20into%20pellets%2C%20which%20are%20moulded%20into%20stylish%20products.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%