0target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Unipads%20Reusable%20Cloth%20Pads%20(%40unipads.in)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98Kalyani%E2%80%99%20network%20was%20born%20%E2%80%94%20village-level%20women%20who%20now%20act%20as%20resellers%20of%20Unipads%2C%20earning%20commissions%20for%20every%20pack%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20women%20in%20Veraval%2C%20just%20getting%20a%20sanitary%20pad%20used%20to%20mean%20travelling%20to%20another%20town.%20So%20when%20they%20began%20selling%20Unipads%20in%20their%20own%20neighbourhoods%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20more%20than%20just%20work%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20freedom.%20They%20weren%E2%80%99t%20just%20looking%20after%20their%20own%20needs%20anymore.%20They%20were%20helping%20friends%2C%20neighbours%2C%20even%20strangers%20feel%20seen%20and%20supported.%20Today%2C%20that%20small%20start%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20network%20of%20over%20190%20Kalyanis%20across%20Gujarat%20%E2%80%94%20each%20playing%20a%20powerful%20role%20in%20changing%20how%20their%20communities%20talk%20about%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20selling%20pads%20was%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20journey.%20Geeta%20and%20her%20team%20made%20sure%20these%20women%20had%20the%20tools%20to%20speak%20with%20confidence.%20They%20trained%20the%20Kalyanis%20not%20only%20in%20product%20knowledge%20but%20also%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F212551%2Ffirst-period-information-pcod-menstruation-pms-menstrual-cups-sanitary-pads-lifestyle-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenstrual%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20knowledge%20that%20many%20of%20them%20had%20never%20received%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnly%20after%20joining%20Unipads%20did%20I%20actually%20understand%20the%20biological%20process%20behind%20menstruation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manisha%2C%20a%20Kalyani%20from%20Veraval.%20%E2